LEX The Shared Root.

"First Person" is a person.
"Swordsman" is a person.
"Mage" is a person.
"Root" is this contract.
"Ground Rules" is a text.
"Trusts" is a text.
"Booted" is a binary.

The First Person appoints the Swordsman, appoints the Mage, fixes the Ground Rules, and fixes the Trusts.

CLAUSE: Rooted.
"Rooted" is defined as: the Ground Rules is fixed and the Trusts is fixed.

CLAUSE: Boot.
The First Person may, if this Root is Rooted: declare Booted.
